product.title: Nippombashi Dori Street Japanese Restaurants Building Sets
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Expand your Little World with a Distinct Touch of Japanese Culture

    Do you miss the diverse, delicious, and affordable Japanese Street Foods? The giant crab, rich drink making, Yakisoba, Yakiimo, Crepes, and more. You can now bring these stores to your city with a range of stores and sets to choose from, to build, role play, and learn how to run Japanese stores in your own comfort room.

    🌸 Measurements varies around 5x5x6in / 13x12x16cm
    🌸 Compatible with leading blocks of standard size (16mm)
    🌸 Each set has over 250 pieces and varies with different sets
    🌸 Excludes original box to protect the environment. For further details please see below.*




    Set 1
    A Japanese Bar, also known as a Katsunuma Vineyard selling drinks.  Japanese loves their Sake (drink). With exquisite details, the drink lid can rotate. It contains over 310 pieces.

    Set 2
    Our second cute     Japanese Restaurant is Osaka Doraku selling their famous specialized crab and seafood. A must-visit place when you go to Japan, look out for the famous gigantic 3d big moving crab billboard. Japanese loves Kani (crab). With the exquisite details. It contains over 330 pieces.

    Set 3
    Our third cute     Japanese Restaurant is an Ippodo Tea Store selling their famous aroma tea. In Japanese, ‘shin’ means new and ‘cha’ means tea. Shincha harvest is in early April when young green tea leaves contain naturally higher concentrations of nutrients and vibrant flavors, the result of wintertime dormancy. With the exquisite details, the roasting mill for tea leaves can turn. It contains over 330 pieces.

     

    Set 4
    Our fourth cute Japanese Restaurant is a Takashi Sushi store selling their most popular dish; Sushi and fresh seafood straight from the ocean. Sushi comes from a Japanese word meaning "sour rice," and it's the rice that's at the heart of sushi. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains over 260 pieces.

    Set 5
    Our fifth cute Japanese Restaurant is Tori Tetsu Yakitori selling a popular mouth-watering dish. Yakitori is a Japanese type of skewered chicken. Its preparation involves skewering the meat with Kushi, a type of skewer typically made of steel, bamboo, or similar materials. Afterward, they are grilled over a charcoal fire. During or after cooking, the meat is typically seasoned with tare sauce or salt.  With the exquisite details as shown. It contains over 300 pieces.

    Set 6
    Our final cute Japanese Restaurant is Kokonoe Agemanju selling their sweets and desserts to complete your meal. They are steamed Manju cakes coated in a tempura batter and deep-fried, so it is hot and sweet. Just be careful not to burn your fingers and your tongue. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains over 310 pieces.

    Our building blocks are designed with advanced engineering features and challenging task for all fans of challenging built, and still achievable to complete by following the instruction booklet.

    The perfect gift for those who love their crafts!

    You will love seeing your family and friends in excitement when they receive our building blocks, leaving an everlasting smile on your loved ones by surprising them with these super innovative and cool building blocks today.

    * Our Building Block sets are packaged in safe and secured protective bags. They do NOT come in the original box to reduce the carbon footprint, save the planet and reduce postage cost on your behalf. It will come with all the pieces and a detailed instruction booklet for you to follow along. If there are missing building blocks please contact us via email at info@kawaiies.com with images of the missing pieces from the booklet.

    Features

    🌸 100% premium quality (ABS) plastic
    🌸 Sharp brilliant colors and solid feel
    🌸 Challenging and rewarding to stimulate all brains
    🌸 High-quality durable non-toxic green material

    WARNING: CHOKING HAZARD - Contain small parts; not suitable for children under 6 years old unless there is adult supervision.

    Standard Blocks: These blocks are compatible with other famous brands.



  • Where do we ship worldwide? Yes, we ship to over 300 countries and proud to provide free shipping to the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, and many countries in Europe.

    What are the blocks made from?     All our building blocks are manufactured from a High-Quality Premium strong, resilient plastic known as acrylonitrile butadiene styrene (ABS) and will stand the test of time and provide hours of fun building their own creations

    Does this help with stress and development?     Our building blocks is a great way to relieve stress and engage in meaningful and joyful conversations. As children comment on their building creations, they develop important communication skills including the ability to explain ideas, describe their work, talk about the process and verbalize challenges that they had along the way. 

    Are these compatible with other leading brands? Yes, these are traditional/standard-sized blocks so they are compatible with other leading brands.

    CHOKING HAZARD: Small parts. Not for children under 6 years old

     

  • We are proud to offer FREE tracked shipping to over 300 countries worldwide including the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many others. If you are wondering if we ship to your country please head over to our Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
